        "setup": "In Canva, open [Account settings](https://www.canva.com/settings/your-account) → your team settings → **SSO & provisioning** → **SCIM**. Enable SCIM user provisioning to mint the token; toggling the switch revokes the old token and creates a new one. Only team admins/owners on Canva for Teams or Education, or eligible Enterprise admins, can generate it.",
